    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>(S) In nomine domini nostri Iehsu Christi eterni dei amen, anno nativitate
                        eius millesimo centesimo optuagesimo sexto, octavo kal. iunii, indictione
                        quarta. Ex huius instrumenti pateat recitatione quod nos <persName
                            ref="#people/3226">Castracane</persName> et <persName><name
                                ref="Castraleo">Castraleo</name></persName> eius filius et
                                <persName><name ref="Adalasia">Adalascia</name></persName> coniux
                        dicti Castraleoni (…) ubi interfuit notitia Uberti iudici ordinarii atque
                        notarii (…) vendimus et tradimus tibi <persName><name ref="Heinricus"
                                >Henrigo</name></persName> filio <persName><name ref="Teminus"
                                >Temini</name></persName> unam nostram terre petiam que hucusque a
                        nobis detinuisti et est posita in plagis et finibus Putei seu in loco ubi
                        dicitur Linari, que terre petiam <rs key="#Wine">vineam</rs> et ficus et <rs
                            key="#Oil">olivas</rs> et alias <rs key="#Fruits/vegetables"
                            >arbores</rs> in se habens. Que tenet unum caput in <rs key="#Rivers"
                            >rivo</rs>, aliud in terra quam detinent <persName><name ref="Wido"
                                >Guidonus</name></persName> et <persName>Salurno</persName> germani
                        quondam <persName><name ref="Tiniosus">Tiniosi</name></persName>, unum
                        laterum in terra et vineam (sic) <persName><name ref="Merollare"
                                >Merollari</name></persName> quondam <persName><name ref="Salomon"
                                >Salomonis</name></persName> at in terra <persName
                            ref="#people/3217">Aldimari</persName> quondam <persName
                            ref="#people/3218">Alberti</persName> et in terra tua qui supra entore.
                        (…) <foreign>Prezzo</foreign>: sexaginta sol. bonorum dinariorum pisani
                        conii. <foreign>Pena</foreign>: in duplum. (…) Actum aput <placeName
                            ref="#places/3210" key="#Rivers #Wine #Oil #Fruits/vegetables"
                            >Puteum</placeName> in domo dictorum venditorum. (…) <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Bernardus">Bernardus</name></persName> quondam
                                <persName><name ref="Widuccius">Guiduci</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Ildebrandinus">Ildibrandinus</name></persName>
                        quondam <persName><name ref="Teutius">Athetii</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Pierus magister de Montefalcone"
                            >Pierus</name></persName> maister de <placeName ref="#places/3202"
                            >Montefalconii</placeName>, suprascripti rogati <rs key="#Witness"
                            >testes</rs> interfuerunt. (S) Ego <persName
                            key="#Writer #Notary #Judge"><name ref="Hubertus"
                            >Hubertus</name></persName> domni imperatoris <rs key="#Judge">iudex
                            ordinarius</rs> atque <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs> post traditam
                        scripsi, comprevi et dedi.</ab>
